productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Montserrat has one of these. She works as a circus performer and she says it looks shriveled.
I tried to maul it but got onion all over it.
My co-worker Reed has one of these. He says it looks microscopic.
heard about this on folktronica radio, decided to give it a try.
I saw one of these in Barbados and I bought one.
